closed_tickets.query: project in (BO,FI) AND type = "Service Request" and created >= "2024-08-07" and created <= "2024-12-31" AND status IN (Closed,"Resolved Non-Approval") AND "it-feol[select list (cascading)]" IS NOT EMPTY ORDER BY created DESC

in_progress_tickets.query: project in (BO,FI) AND type = "Service Request" and created >= "2024-08-07" and created <= "2024-12-31" AND status IN ("Escalated Non-Approval") AND "it-feol[select list (cascading)]" IS NOT EMPTY ORDER BY created DESC

canceled_tickets.query: project in (BO,FI) AND type = "Service Request" and created >= "2024-08-07" and created <= "2024-12-31" AND status IN ("Canceled") AND "it-feol[select list (cascading)]" IS NOT EMPTY ORDER BY created DESC

royalty_tickets.query: project in (TC) ORDER BY created DESC
